@AbdallahgalalAg @lufthansa Hello Abdallah, 
I'm sorry to hear you've been left with that impression. Kindly send us the reference number (XXXX-OS-XXXXX) of your claim per DM and we'll see what we can do. 
Best regards, Gayle

@lalanishayaan Hello Shayaan,
we're very sorry for any inconvenience concerning your request. Thank you for your patience until now. We kindly ask you to give our colleagues more time as they try to accomplish every case individually.
Best regards, Alessandra

@kivavala1 Hi Audra, 
Thank you for getting in touch. We are sorry to hear about this inconvenience. Please be informed that we have replied to your PM already. Please check your inbox or notifications. Thank you for your patience. 
Best regards, Shawn

@duzdanisaq Hello Ismail,
kindly send your request to impressum@austrian.com, stating the fact that it was impossible to fill out the form online. Please be advised that using the provided e-mail is only a workaround.
Best regards, Gayle

@abdullatif_aydn @EAES_eu @claimcompanies @Flight_Refunds (2/2) they are currently unable to adhere to on their normal response time. 
Best regards
Alessandra

@gabrieleromano_ @lufthansa Hello Gabriele,
I'm sorry to hear that you have been affected by a flight delay. Please send us your booking code via DM and we'll see what we can do for you. 
Best regards, Gayle

@solotravelstory Hallo Carolin,
wir können Dir in diesem Fall leider nicht weiterhelfen. Bitte bleibe in Kontakt mit dem zuständigen Team von Lost &amp; Found in Berlin. 
Viele Grüße, Alessandra

@mtsullivn Hello Mike, 
Apologies for all the inconvenience. Have you filed a claim already? If yes, please send me the reference number (XXXX-OS-XXXXX) via DM, and I'll have a closer look. 
Best regards, Gayle

@ivaanvuckovic Hello Ivan, please send us your booking code in a DM. We will check the reservation.
Best regards
Alessandra

@JessicaJagec @eDreams @united Hello Jessica, 
Once you have filled out the online form, your request will be directed to the respective department. Please be assured that my colleagues will process your request. 
Best regards, Gayle

@BillyBog1 Hi there, 
please be so kind and use the following link in order to submit your delayed or lost luggage report. Our respective colleagues will get in touch with you as soon as they have any information. Thank you for your understanding.
Best regards, Shawn

@lenniezhu Hello Lennie, 
I'm sorry to hear about your experience. Feel free to send your feedback to our Feedback Management via this online form https://t.co/iSWK3YFadl 
Best regards, Gayle
